{"title":"Want to ride Tom Pidcock’s actual bike? This is your chance","link":"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/ineos-bikes-for-sale","date":1678193110000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/ineos-bikes-for-sale\">Want to ride Tom Pidcock’s actual bike? This is your chance</a></p>\n\n<p>Danish cycling shop CYKOM is launching an online sale of race-used equipment from the Ineos Grenadiers team including bikes from the likes of Geraint Thomas and Tom Pidcock.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"970\" height=\"752\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/03/Egan-Bernal-Dogma-970x752.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/03/Egan-Bernal-Dogma-970x752.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/03/Egan-Bernal-Dogma-300x233.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/03/Egan-Bernal-Dogma-768x595.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/03/Egan-Bernal-Dogma-1536x1191.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/03/Egan-Bernal-Dogma-2048x1588.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/03/Egan-Bernal-Dogma-750x581.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/03/Egan-Bernal-Dogma-1140x884.jpg 1140w\" /><figcaption>Egan Bernal’s Pinarello Dogma, CYKOM</figcaption><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Items for sale include various Pinarello Dogma F bikes with <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/shimano-dura-ace-r9200-groupset-review\" target=\"_blank\">Shimano Dura-Ace Di2</a> and Lightweight or Shimano wheels, some with personalised features from the riders themselves, like name decals. Also available will be Filippo Ganna’s original TT-world champion helmet, team clothing and components. So if you want to ride like a world champion, a <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/tags/tour-de-france\" target=\"_blank\">Tour de France</a> winner or an Olympic gold medalist, now’s your chance.</p>\n\n\n<div>\r\n                <div>\r\n                   <div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <h3><span>Related Posts</span></h3>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <div>\r\n                            <div>\r\n                            <article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h3>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/pro-bikes-for-sale-bike-room\">Want to ride an actual pro bike? Bike Room has you covered</a>\r\n                       </h3>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h3>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/pinarello-dogma-f-disc-review\">Pinarello Dogma F Disc review</a>\r\n                       </h3>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h3>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/pinarello-dogma-f-ineos-pidcock-bike\">Tour de France bikes: Tom Pidcock’s Pinarello Dogma F</a>\r\n                       </h3>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h3>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/worldtour-team-bikes\">WorldTour team bikes 2023: Cyclist’s complete guide</a>\r\n                       </h3>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article></div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <span></span><span></span><span></span>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <div></div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <div></div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        </div>\n\n\n<p>On 8<sup>th</sup> March 2023 at 21:00 CET (8pm UK), fans will be able to buy selected bikes, clothing and other items from the professional cycling team through CYKOM’s <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/s/liveshopping-team-ineos-releas/1279164549340929/\" target=\"_blank\">hour-long live sale</a> on Facebook. CYKOM will broadcast live in Danish from 7:30pm – 8:30pm, followed by an English broadcast from 9pm to 10pm (GMT+1).</p>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"647\" height=\"970\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/03/geraint-thomas-bike-cykom-647x970.jpeg\" alt=\"Thomas decal on seat tube of bike\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/03/geraint-thomas-bike-cykom-647x970.jpeg 647w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/03/geraint-thomas-bike-cykom-200x300.jpeg 200w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/03/geraint-thomas-bike-cykom-768x1152.jpeg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/03/geraint-thomas-bike-cykom-1024x1536.jpeg 1024w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/03/geraint-thomas-bike-cykom-1365x2048.jpeg 1365w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/03/geraint-thomas-bike-cykom-750x1125.jpeg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/03/geraint-thomas-bike-cykom-1140x1710.jpeg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/03/geraint-thomas-bike-cykom.jpeg 1707w\" /><figcaption>CYKOM</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>Founded in 2016 as ProOwnedCycling, CYKOM claims to be the first company of its kind, buying equipment from WorldTour teams to then sell to customers. Additionally, CYKOM has also reached an agreement with Tour de France organisers ASO to sell merchandise on site at many ASO events.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tempted? We can’t promise buying one of these bikes will give you <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/tom-pidcock-descending-safa-brian\" target=\"_blank\">Tom Pidcock’s descending skills</a>, however.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/ineos-bikes-for-sale\">Want to ride Tom Pidcock’s actual bike? This is your chance</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a>.</p>","author":"Robyn Davidson &#124; Editorial Assistant","siteTitle":"Cyclist.co.uk","siteHash":"561486e7070fa5351de9318ad0fa26c2a39332acba5fc7c7d1694a01d53d431e","entryHash":"446d8c211039c2e0229d89b8a6e0263e018b9d3c5c4fb38b463d76a3bcb52ece","category":"Cycling"}